a(S'Modern[edit]'
p1998
g2
tp1999
a(S'Intertwined with this story of indigenous art, are movements of painting, sculpture, and architecture such as the Hudson River School and the Ashcan School of the 19th century, and Pop Art and Abstract Expressionism of the 20th. Some of the most celebrated images were produced by artists of the American West, featuring \x93Cowboys and Indians,\x94 and some of the most visually complex objects were created by African Americans.'
